fullText: [Sister Mary & self at home alone - Julia at her home Churchville--] Visited Mrs Miller - Geneva - to be with Hattie Stanton & her daughter Nora $300
summaryText: Susan B. Anthony visited Mrs. Miller in Geneva with Sister Mary and was accompanied by Hattie Stanton and her daughter Nora. She also mentions Julia being at her home in Churchville. She notes a financial transaction of $300.
